Hudson’s getting some play time in with his new toy while we finish decorating the tree! #ad We went into @walmart to get this new @officialblueytv Bluey Ultimate Lights & Sounds Playhouse! His new favorite toy for sure!  Bluey's house comes to life when you press the Octopus in the kids’ room to activate lights and over 50 sounds and phrases! And you can even attach the figures to the dance floor and move the lever to create a little show! Love that it closes up and this playset is huge at a whopping 17" tall and 30" wide when you open it up! There are three stories to explore - all fully furnished with the same furniture seen in the TV show! Perfect toy for your Bluey loving little one this holiday
 season!  @supermoosetoys  #socialspotters #Bluey

Well we’ve been keeping a secret for a few months.  We are already almost halfway there to adding another little one to our family! Thanks to the people that have known and kept it a secret for us. We do know the gender. This was so unexpected for us and has taken some adjustment for me to accept but regardless we can’t wait to add another little one to our bunch. 💛

I can’t believe it’s time to start transitioning Hudson into the next room to start making his old room a nursery once again. It’s still a work in progress as we still obviously have Hudson’s things on the wall but slowly collecting stuff for baby as we’re about half way through is nice. This beautiful crib from @deltachildren is everything though. I love the colors and how well it fits the space. 😍 Hudson is so excited to be a big brother. 💛
Figured it was probably about time to announce that our new addition to the family is another little boy 💚💙
